Package: SpatialGraphRefine
Type: Package
Title: Fast Spatial Refinement of Cluster Labels
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano", family = "Cacciatore",
    email = "tkcaccia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Refines noisy spatial cluster labels with a fast, boundary-aware nearest-
    neighbor graph or local support-vector-machine style decision boundaries. The C++
    implementation supports large two- and three-dimensional spatial transcriptomics
    datasets, multiple tissue sections, simulation, diagnostics, and high-resolution
    projection. Large datasets can be processed as overlapping two- or three-
    dimensional tiles on multiple CPU workers. Optional CUDA and Metal providers can
    register through a stable backend interface. A legacy SVM interface is retained.
